				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BA%A1c-Nh%E1%BA%A1c-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%C3%A0nh-h%E1%BA%A1/poem-BAsfMtb6QcvQC4GU52sPzA">Bạc Nhạc Dương thành hạ - 泊岳陽城下</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Cung/C%C3%B4n-L%C3%B4n-ng%E1%BB%A5c-trung-k%C3%BD-T%E1%BA%ADp-Xuy%C3%AAn-ti%C3%AAn-sinh/poem-3T4BcZps8Bv7oXYdK1vCnQ">Côn Lôn ngục trung ký Tập Xuyên tiên sinh - 崑崙獄中寄集川先生</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Cung/author-35Vn44AjbUjdch-9xsSRRg">Trần Trọng Cung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/D%C6%B0-l%E1%BB%B1c-h%E1%BB%8Dc-v%C4%83n/poem-Mg8rPh0z48bJyipa1yDGrQ">Dư lực học văn - 餘力學文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/author-Q1iBAvdMoGVZdNIyHAuy-w">Lý Dục Tú</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/L%C3%A3o-lai/poem-KgtZgZ3P9HbcgFyIsCNzAA">Lão lai - 老來</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/author-h_HbFCmxWKkwxboqzaEfNA">Trần Nguyên Đán</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Hi%E1%BA%BFu/Qu%C3%A1-D%E1%BA%A1-Tr%E1%BA%A1ch-ch%C3%A2u/poem-hjcQ051sma3Pgt7N_w_HZA">Quá Dạ Trạch châu - 過夜澤州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Hi%E1%BA%BFu/author-ve1xEueifA2JFPvjBvrK4g">Nguyễn Khắc Hiếu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/T%E1%BA%A1p-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-Y2iPZ0BGjE-jLf0TRR_XTg">Tạp thi kỳ 2 - 雜詩其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/author-_plJ3nwj8cVN02KPZ4P_8g">Tào Phi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/T%E1%BB%91ng-nh%C3%A2n/poem-cFaiJWajT_3vfsAWKg1raQ">Tống nhân - 送人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Th%C3%B4i/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-linh-c%E1%BB%95-s%E1%BA%AFt/poem-VnWT9gPBhXHsog6eFUt8mA">Tương linh cổ sắt - 湘靈鼓瑟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Th%C3%B4i/author-KDKOma9Y1p2EXiiYHNKvMQ">Nguỵ Thôi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-C%C6%A1/Vi-C%E1%BB%91-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-Ti%C3%AAn-t%E1%BA%B7ng-ph%E1%BB%A5-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-bGdQDSjh1WP4i6FluaMuQw">Vi Cố Ngạn Tiên tặng phụ kỳ 1 - 為顧彥先贈婦其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-C%C6%A1/author-EfNc8fssq4nwf0WjqNOWdA">Lục Cơ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-3mvgQ8jqLVNdE0oNQACUCg">Vịnh hoài kỳ 2 - 詠懷其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
